&lt;li&gt;Enforce and enhance safety protocols, ensuring compliance with industry standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage project budgets, schedules, and timelines to ensure successful project completion.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engage from project reimplementation through mobilization to project completion.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Direct involvement in ground-up construction, especially during the foundation phase.&lt;/li&gt;
